18:03.706 --> 18:05.470
- The police are on their way.
- Listen... listen...

18:05.472 --> 18:07.040
Okay. I am the...
I'm with the...

18:07.042 --> 18:08.475
The police
will be here momentarily.

18:08.477 --> 18:09.641
