that looked out of place?

18:44.578 --> 18:47.246
So, how old exactly?

18:47.248 --> 18:50.182
Oh, I'd say
he was about 50 or 60?

18:50.184 --> 18:52.552
- Closer to 60?
- Yeah.

18:52.554 --> 18:56.859
- Or 50?
- Yeah. Uh, 50 to 60.

18:57.892 --> 18:59.661
Sound about right
to you, John?

19:00.495 --> 19:01.897
Mm-hmm.

19:09.371 --> 19:11.304
So what happened?

19:11.306 --> 19:12.971
Are you guys, okay?

19:12.973 --> 19:15.074
Um...

19:15.076 --> 19:16.376
