19:23.818 --> 19:25.686
- You did what he said.
- Yes!

19:25.688 --> 19:29.757
- Because he said he had a gun.
- Yes. And also...

19:31.892 --> 19:34.796
I mean, he was also
sort of a gentleman.

20:17.105 --> 20:19.639
She don't speak
a lick of English.

20:19.641 --> 20:22.774
And I don't know but one
