every time I turn around.

21:54.169 --> 21:56.805
Okay. You can quit.

21:57.872 --> 21:59.741
Or you can try and catch 'em.

22:14.623 --> 22:16.959
I didn't think
you'd ever actually call.

22:18.293 --> 22:20.627
I didn't think you'd pick up.
So we're even.

22:22.229 --> 22:24.497
- So, how's your truck?
