22:27.169 --> 22:28.700
You've been traveling
a lot, I guess?

22:28.702 --> 22:30.035
Oh, yeah.

22:30.037 --> 22:31.603
Selling a lot of Bibles?

22:31.605 --> 22:32.971
Yeah. A whole lot.

22:32.973 --> 22:34.873
You're looking at one
of the top five salesmen

22:34.875 --> 22:36.409
in the area right here.

22:36.411 --> 22:37.813
- Yeah?
- Yup.

22:39.148 --> 22:41.350
I don't believe
a word you say.

22:42.284 --> 22:43.752
Probably a good idea.

22:46.653 --> 22:48.455
You aren't wearing
your hearing aid.

22:48.457 --> 22:49.855
Hmm?

22:49.857 --> 22:51.757
You're not wearing
your hearing aid!

22:51.759 --> 22:53.092
I'm sorry, I can't hear ya.

22:53.094 --> 22:54.459
You're not wearing your...

22:54.461 --> 22:55.998
God.

22:58.933 --> 23:01.936
Hey. Got something for ya.

23:07.342 --> 23:08.443
John Hunt!

23:09.209 --> 23:12.014
John Hunt, where is he?
There he is.

23:12.847 --> 23:15.081
Looks like your
rainy-day robber is at it again.

23:15.083 --> 23:18.083
Laugh it up, Columbo.
What do you got?

23:18.085 --> 23:21.920
Gene Dentler sent that over.
Said it made him think of you.

23:21.922 --> 23:24.055
That's hilarious.

23:24.057 --> 23:25.358
Don't you worry about it, man.

23:25.360 --> 23:27.963
I've already got the AARP
on the case.

23:32.566 --> 23:33.867
Hello. Gene.

23:33.869 --> 23:35.434
Hey, Gene Dentler.
It's John Hunt here.

23:35.436 --> 23:36.836
<i>Tell me about this robbery.</i>

23:36.838 --> 23:38.571
Oh, you mean the old guy?

23:38.573 --> 23:42.774
Yeah, same story. Small haul.
No prints, no MO, no nothing.

23:42.776 --> 23:44.476
So you got no leads, huh?

23:44.478 --> 23:45.879
What a fucking surprise.

23:45.881 --> 23:48.380
Mainly on account
of nobody giving a shit.

23:48.382 --> 23:50.749
It's just kind
of a funny story.

23:50.751 --> 23:53.285
Yeah. Nothing funnier
than armed robbery.

23:53.287 --> 23:54.920
<i>Yeah.</i>

23:54.922 --> 23:56.555
<i>Oh, you know,
speaking of funny...</i>

23:56.557 --> 23:58.957
here's where
it gets interesting.

23:58.959 --> 24:01.159
I told my wife
about the whole deal.

24:01.161 --> 24:02.829
And I guess
she tells her sister,

24:02.831 --> 24:05.063
'cause the next day,
her sister calls me

24:05.065 --> 24:07.600
and she told me about a thing
she read in the paper

24:07.602 --> 24:09.636
that sounds real similar.

24:09.638 --> 24:11.871
Old guy... with a gun.

24:11.873 --> 24:15.076
Oh, yeah? What's your, uh,
your wife's sister's name?

24:16.478 --> 24:17.643
