I'm calling about

24:17.645 --> 24:18.945
this robbery you had
on June 8th.

24:18.947 --> 24:20.880
Is that case still open?

24:22.216 --> 24:24.584
Yes, ma'am. Would you fax it
to me? Thank you.

24:25.353 --> 24:27.555
Now, what do you mean
when you say more than one?

24:28.989 --> 24:29.989
Two?

24:34.062 --> 24:35.794
Excuse me.

24:35.796 --> 24:36.862
- Oh, hi.
- Hi.

24:36.864 --> 24:38.296
I'd like to open up
an account.

24:38.298 --> 24:41.766
